  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the cost(effectiveness) of three existing antibiotic
      strategies for patients with community-acquired pneumonia admitted to the hospital, but not
      the ICU.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
